      "description": "Raw and reduced experimental data from two-laboratory ASTM F1717 static compression-bending campaign. Eleven constructs tested; includes load-displacement traces, stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement. Dataset was compiled and locked prior to the minor mesh-refinement revision applied to the FEA model in November 2025. The modeling team judged the revision to affect only element size in the rod-screw interface fillet region and considered the change not material to the dataset's relevance; formal re-validation against the revised model build was deferred pending the next annual review cycle.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-09T00:00:00Z",
